{"tid":2128487,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"傳滙控評估中美衝突升溫衝擊聯匯影響，研究出售歐美業務","createTime":"2020-07-28T04:18:21.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-28T05:38:33.000Z","uid":28114,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"cac3c3dd2771c4141570f98d0bbda7eac3baeae9","tid":2128487,"uid":28114,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-28T04:18:21.000Z","msg":"　　《經濟通通訊社２８日專訊》據彭博社引述知情人士報道指，匯豐控股（００００５）主席<br />\n杜嘉祺正全面審查歐洲與美國的業務，並及研究出售相關業務的可能性，以應對中美衝突可能持<br />\n續升溫。<br />\n　　消息指，匯控高層與英倫銀行高層商談時表示，擔心香港聯繫滙率可能受干預，故出售歐美<br />\n業務是應對措施之一。<br />\n　　日前中國《人民日報》指控匯豐參與構陷、協助美國捏造罪證陷害華為首席財務官孟晚舟，<br />\n雖然其後匯豐發聲明否認，但央視旗下中國環球電視網之後訪問知情人士指，孟晚舟２０１３年<br />\n與匯豐高層的會面是由匯豐提出，而非由華為提出。（ａｌ）<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.etnet.com.hk/www/tc/news/categorized_news_detail.php?category=latest&amp;newsid=ETN300728237\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.etnet.com.hk%2Fwww%2Ftc%2Fnews%2Fcategorized_news_detail.php%3Fcategory%3Dlatest%26newsid%3DETN300728237&d=oFI5KSBgBGvHra6dYUznBtjJpSEh9fPrneULq4V%2BA60%3D&h=bc02c72c\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.etnet.com.hk/www/tc/news/categorized_news_detail.php?category=latest&amp;newsid=ETN300728237</a>"},{"pid":"9167be0c364a46c81cd3c6b15faa65eb8a17981a","tid":2128487,"uid":28114,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-28T04:20:15.000Z","msg":"Squeezed by Superpowers, HSBC Eyes Next Step of Endless Reboot<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2020-07-27/squeezed-by-superpowers-hsbc-eyes-next-step-of-endless-reboot\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bloomberg.com%2Fnews%2Farticles%2F2020-07-27%2Fsqueezed-by-superpowers-hsbc-eyes-next-step-of-endless-reboot&d=oFI5KSBgBGvHra6dYUznBtjJpSEh9fPrneULq4V%2BA60%3D&h=69804815\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2020-07-27/squeezed-by-superpowers-hsbc-eyes-next-step-of-endless-reboot</a>"},{"pid":"62f8c9f5c98b3ccbd9dad7ad556b32d3677f084c","tid":2128487,"uid":21493,"like":0,"dislike":0,"s